Dependencies
------------

Please make sure you have the following development libraries
installed in your system:

   *  libxml2
   *  libdb (Berkeley DB)


Compilation from source
-----------------------

You will need the GNU packages automake and libtool installed in your system
to compile 00mnik.

1. Run the script

  ./auto_init.sh

  to create all supporting files of autotools.


2.  ./configure

   to create the Makefile.


3. make

   to compile.

To get back to the bare source distribution you can run
the "auto_cleanup.sh" script to remove the autotools files.
